# QA MODE: POST-BUILD SEMANTIC REVIEW

> **TL;DR:** The `/qa` command performs a structured semantic review of code implemented during BUILD mode against the original plan. It catches over-engineering, incomplete implementations, pattern violations, and implementation debris that mechanical checks cannot detect. Required for L2+ tasks; gates `/reflect`.

